Package com.chembiohub.tpmap.dstruct

Class Protein1DLogistic

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.chembiohub.tpmap.dstruct.Protein1DLogistic
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Protein
    @Deprecated
public class Protein1DLogistic
extends java.lang.Object
implements Protein
    Deprecated.
    This class uses a 6-parameter Logistic curve fit, this has now been depreciated in favour of a TP1dDenaturationFunction in Protein1D
    Protein1DLogistic The Protein1D class defines an individual protein, including it's accession, name, organism name, description. This class also holds 2x2 matrices for each Replicate x TMT for: - Absolute values - Relative values - Relative values normalised TP-MAP scores and P-values are stored for the protein.
